                        "displayName": "Wes McKinney",
                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "America/New_York"
                    },
                    "body": "It might be acceptable to have a slower, but smaller (in code size) implementation. For example, simply transposing the negative indices to be positive and then invoking the non-negative-Take implementation",
